description	"Rakatan Infernal Lord

^2Weaponry:
- Single Lightsaber
-- Saber Defense (3)
-- Blaster Defense (2)

^5Force Powers:
- Jump (3)
- Pull (2)
- Push (2)
- Lightning (3)
- Drain (2)

^8Attributes:
- Rakatan Strength 3 (Heavy melee, Wookiee Health)
- Force Block (2)
- Force Focus (1)

Investigation after the destruction of the Star Forge revealed that the scarred world of Leheron held an ancient being who was at the forefront of the
Infinite Empire. Upon learning about the current state of the Galaxy, the Infernal One decided that he would join the Sith Empire.
Rakatans are attuned to the Dark Side of the Force and use it to selfishly strengthen themselves over the benefit of others.
"